item.title: Final prototype
item.description: Final prototype September 5, 2021 Finally after more than a year and a half, I finished my industrial prototype. As I mentioned before, the unit should have been 16 feet long in order to be as productive as possible (length of panels normally). I was running out of space, and wanted to save money, so I made a smaller one. The whole system The whole system side view Your browser does not support video.
